Park Square Raises $1.2 Billion for Buyout Fund, FT Reports

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-04-05T04:18:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/park-square-raises-1-2-billion-for-buyout-fund-ft-reports.html
Park Square Capital LLP has raised
850 million euros ($1.2 billion) for a fund that will be
invested in loans for leveraged buyouts, the Financial Times
reported.  A third of the fund has already been allocated to seven
transactions and the rest will be invested over five years, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in  London  on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 